text: Daylight robbery..ordered through food delivery platform. $6.80 ban mian hardly any ingredient, few tiny ikan billis. I opted to add fishball..they charged $2.50 for 1 fishball!!!

This did not seem to taste as well as the last time I patronised this stall... but that was more than a year ago.

Added $1 worth of additional thick bee hoon - It was too much!
